






課程名稱：前瞻類比積體電路設計








 
Advanced Analog Integrated Circuits (6895)
 
課程特色
ý        
研究所進階課程。
ý        
進階類比積體電路之介紹與分析。
ý        
學習類比電路理論，並結合電路設計、模擬與驗證的技巧。
ý        
熟悉各式類比積體電路應用電路的設計考量。
課程大綱
1.              
Basic Opamp Design (note)
2.              
Advanced Opamp Design (note)
3.              
Comparators (note)
4.              
Sample and Holds (note)
5.              
Switched-Capacitor Circuits (note)
6.              
Data Converters (Nyquist-Rate D/A
& A/D) (note)
7.              
Oversampling Converter
8.              
Continuous-Time Filters
9.              
Phase-Locked Loops (note)
10.        
High-Speed Circuit Design (Selective topic)
Textbook
David A. Johns
and Ken Martin, Analog Integrated Circuit Design, Wiley, 1997.
References
1.              
Rudy van de Plassche, CMOS
Integrated Analog-to-Digital and Digital-to-Analog Converters, 2nd
Edition, Kluwer, 2003.
2.              
B. Razavi, Design of Integrated
Circuits for Optical Communications, McGraw Hill, 2003.
3.              
Phillip E. Allen and Douglas R. Holberg,
CMOS Circuit Design, Oxford,
2002.
4.              
Technical Papers
Final Scores: will be determined by
1.              
Homework  20%
2.              
Mid-Term exam.  40%
3.              
Final Project  40%
CAD Tools: Hspice, etc.
 










課程名稱：前瞻類比積體電路設計






 
Advanced Analog Integrated Circuits (6895)
 
課程特色
ý        
研究所進階課程。
ý        
進階類比積體電路之介紹與分析。
ý        
學習鎖相迴路理論，並結合電路設計、模擬與驗證的技巧。
ý        
熟悉各式鎖相迴路積體電路應用電路的設計考量。
課程大綱
1.              
Fundamentals of PLLs (note1, note2, note3)
2.              
Concepts of
oscillators (note4)
3.              
Charge-pump
phase-locked loops (note5)
4.              
Behavior of
phase-locked loops (note6)
5.              
Clocking
Techniques (note7, note8,
note9)
6.              
LC-type
Oscillators
7.              
Frequency
Synthesizers (note10)
8.              
Clock
and Data Recovery
References
1.              
Floyd M. Gardner, Phaselock
Techniques, 3rd Edition, Wiley, 2005.
2.              
B. Razavi, Design of Integrated
Circuits for Optical Communications, McGraw Hill, 2003.
3.              
劉深淵、楊清淵, 鎖相迴路, 滄海書局, 2006.
4.              
Technical Papers
Final Scores: will be determined by
1.              
Homework 
2.              
Mid-Term exam.  
3.              
Final Project  
CAD Tools: Hspice, Matlab, etc.
 



 



