課程概述 / Course Description
由於高速資料傳輸的需求日益增加，使得無線和有線通信蓬勃起來，擴展高速元件和電路設計的工作視野。本課程將針對通信系統中的高速積體電路的分析和設計作為教材，以培養前瞻性積體電路設計之人才。
The increasing demand for high-speed tansport of data has revitalized wireless and wireline communications, leading to extensive work on high-speed device and circuit design. The course addresses the need for tutorial materials dealing with the analysis and design of high-speed integrated circuits (ICs) for communication systems and prove advanced IC design to students.
 
課程目標 / Course Objextives
本課程是提供學生對於高速電路與系統設計和分析的準備工夫，進而邁向通信積體電路設計的務實應用。
The course is intended to prepare the students for design and analysis of high-speed circuits and systems, and to pursue more practical applications on communication IC design.
 
教科書

        1.Behzad Razavi, Design of Integrated Circuits for Optical Communications, McGraw-Hill, 2003.
      
 
